Project Structure Overview
todo-app/
├── .env                  # Backend environment variables (MongoDB URI)
├── package.json          # Backend dependencies (express, mongoose, dotenv, cors)
├── server.js             # Backend server (Express & Mongoose logic)
└── frontend/             # React application created with npx create-react-app
    └── src/
        ├── App.js        # Main component for fetching data and managing state
        ├── AddTodo.js    # Component to add new tasks
        ├── TodoList.js   # Component to list, toggle, and manage tasks
        └── EditTodo.js   # Component for editing a task's text
        └── ...           # (Other standard React files like index.js, App.css, etc.)
